“Banan” so‘zi almashtirilsin:

txt = "I like bananas"

x = txt.replace("bananas", "apples")

print(x)

Ta'rifi va qo'llanilishi
Usul replace()belgilangan iborani boshqa belgilangan ibora bilan almashtiradi.

Eslatma: Agar boshqa hech narsa ko'rsatilmagan bo'lsa, ko'rsatilgan iboraning barcha holatlari almashtiriladi.

Sintaksis
string.replace(oldvalue, newvalue, count)

Parametr qiymatlari
Parameter	Description
oldvalue ----	Required. The string to search for
newvalue ----	Required. The string to replace the old value with
count	 ----   Optional. A number specifying how many occurrences of the old value you want to replace. Default is all occurrences


Misol
“Bir” so‘zining barcha ko‘rinishlari almashtirilsin:

txt = "one one was a race horse, two two was one too."

x = txt.replace("one", "three")

print(x)

Misol
“Bir” so‘zining birinchi ikkita ko‘rinishi almashtirilsin:

txt = "one one was a race horse, two two was one too."

x = txt.replace("one", "three", 2)

print(x)